-- Audi in Talks to Buy Luxury Motorcycle Maker Ducati
-- B y
-- 2012-03-13T12:17:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-13/audi-in-talks-to-buy-luxury-motorcycle-maker-ducati.html
Bloomberg's  Erik Schatzker  reports 
that Audi AG  is in talks to buy Ducati Motor Holding SpA, the 
maker of luxury motorbikes ridden by celebrities such as Brad 
Pitt, from owner Investindustrial SpA, according to two people 
familiar with the matter. He speaks on Bloomberg Television's 
"Inside Track." (Source: Bloomberg)  Running Time: 00:51
 